It would be nice to have multiple timetracking fields that can be used.  Specifically, on our projects we like to have a Team Lead Estimate field that is used for leads to give an estimate of the amount of work required for a given issue.  This value is used (in an XP fashion) to develop a velocity for Team Lead estimates, and thereby predict the amount of work that can be put into a release.
